<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title><%= app_name() %></title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        background: #fafafa;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container { text-align: center; max-width: 28rem; padding: 2rem; }
      h1 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      p { margin: 0.5rem 0; color: #666; font-size: 1rem; }
      a { color: #597099; }
      .ja { margin-top: 1.5rem; border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5; padding-top: 1.5rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Something went wrong loading <%= app_name() %>.</h1>
      <p>Try refreshing the page.</p>
      <p><a href="/">Return home</a></p>

      <div class="ja" lang="ja">
        <h1><%= app_name() %>の読み込みで問題が発生しました。</h1>
        <p>ページを更新してみてください。</p>
        <p><a href="/">ホームに戻る</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
